          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections for the (g,n) reaction in Cu63,  Cu65,",
                " Zn64, Sb121 and Pr141 have been measured.",
                "The 63Cu(gamma,n)  cross  section  results  for   the",
                " lithium   radiation   confirm   the   bremsstrahlung",
                " measurement of the shape of the cross section values",
                " are 25% lower.",
                "Comparison of  cross   sections   for   the   lithium",
                " resonance   radiation   for  Cu-65,  Zn-64,  Sb-121,",
                " Pr-141,  measured relative to that  of  Cu-63,  with",
                " previous results suggests that discrepancies are due",
                " to inaccuracies in absolute beta-counting."
              ]
            }
          ],
